&quot;Augmentative and alternative communication (AAC) is an umbrella term that encompasses the communication methods used to supplement or replace speech or writing for those with impairments in the production or comprehension of spoken or written language.&quot; - Wikipedia

These apps can be used by anyone who has problems communicating due to some sort of physical or mental disability. These apps are also for all ages and can be life changing for people who struggle with communicating their needs.

